    "description": {
        "en-US": "v 3.1.1, morat edition\n- three year hiatus/TB60 recovery [fix by morat]\n- thanks to Tina Becker for leading me to the fix\n\nv 3.1\n- option to expand all threads [thanks to jpfle]\n- fixed apply button issues\n\nv 3.0\n- sort precedence [thanks to Realraven]\n- options dialog overhaul [thanks to Realraven]\n- backward compatibility\n\nv 2.1c\n- toggle/sort hidden column [thanks to romkyns]\n\nv 2.1b\n- fixed sort issue in options.js [thanks to romkyns]\n- changed the method of detecting a sortable column\n\nv 2.1a\n- 'Apply' button added to options dialog\n\nv 2.1\n- active element search indicator\n- Expression Search / GMailUI fix\n- tab clean-up after close fix\n\nv 2.0\n- toggle unthreaded (options) [thanks to roasted]\n- custom column sorting (options)\n- \"Apply columns to search as list\" menu\n- facet tab replaced with search indicator\n- setTimeout changed to setInterval\n- minor bugfixes\n\nv 1.2a\n- random number bugfix for multiple same searches\n- unintended button removed quickfilter toolbar\n- tab tooltip updated\n- minor bugfixes\n\nv 1.2\n- return to facet view with shift+close [x]\n- auto open list view when only few results are found (options) [thanks to :wsmwk]\n- custom column configurations (options) [thanks to bernd]\n- minor bugfixes\n\nv 1.1\n- support for search by email and tag [thanks to stefahn &amp; :wsmwk]\n- reduced timeout interval"
    },
